<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Ella Rises</title>

    <!-- Brand Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background: #F9F5EA; /* brand cream */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* NAVBAR ---------------------------------------------------- */

        .navbar {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            background: #F9F5EA;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #FFD8D1;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 10;
            align-items: center;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .nav-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 24px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .nav-right {
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .navbar a {
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .nav-brand {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #3A3F3B;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: #3A3F3B;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
            color: #CE325B;
        }

        .nav-login {
            background: #F9AFB1;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: #3A3F3B;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-login:hover {
            background: #F4B092;
        }

        /* HEADER ---------------------------------------------------- */

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px 40px 20px;
        }

        .site-title {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #3A3F3B;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #CE325B;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        /* HERO ------------------------------------------------------ */

        .hero {
            background: #FFD8D1; /* soft blush */
            padding: 40px 20px;
            border-radius: 0 0 30px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #3A3F3B;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 24px auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-main {
            background: #F9AFB1;
            color: #3A3F3B;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn-main:hover {
            background: #F4B092;
        }

        /* SECTION ---------------------------------------------------- */

        .section {
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .section:nth-child(even) {
            background: #FFF;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #3A3F3B;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* PROGRAM CARDS --------------------------------------------- */

        .programs {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 32px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .prog-card {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border: 2px solid #9AB59D;
            border-radius: 16px;
            width: 260px;
            height: 430px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }

        .prog-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #F9F5EA;
        }

        .prog-content {
            padding: 16px 14px;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .prog-card h3 {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            color: #3A3F3B;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .prog-card p {
            color: #3A3F3B;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            line-height: 1.45;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .prog-card .btn-small {
            background: #F9AFB1;
            color: #3A3F3B;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 18px auto 22px auto;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .prog-card .btn-small:hover {
            background: #F4B092;
        }

        /* FOOTER ---------------------------------------------------- */

        footer {
            background: #3A3F3B;
            color: #F9F5EA;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px 10px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #F9AFB1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Full-width area with background image or color */
        .donate-bg {
            background: url('/images/logos/donate.png') center/cover no-repeat;
            /* Fallback shade if image not loaded yet */
            background-color: #FFD8D1;
            padding: 90px 20px;
            margin-top: 0px;
            border-radius: 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* White card */
        .donate-card {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
            border: 2px solid #F9F5EA;
        }

        /* Title */
        .donate-card h2 {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #3A3F3B;
        }

        /* Text */
        .donate-card p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            line-height: 1.65;
            color: #3A3F3B;
            max-width: 620px;
            margin: 0 auto 32px auto;
        }

        /* Buttons layout */
        .donate-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 22px;
        }

        /* Donate button */
        .btn-donateD {
            background: #F9AFB1;
            color: #3A3F3B;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-donateD:hover {
            background: #F4B092;
        }

        /* Impact button */
        .btn-impactD {
            background: #F9F5EA;
            color: #3A3F3B;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-impactD:hover {
            background: #FFFFFF;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- NAVBAR -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-left">
            <a href="/" class="nav-brand">Ella Rises</a>
            <a href="/viewPart" class="nav-link">Participants</a>
            <% if (level === "m") { %>
            <a href="/viewUsers" class="nav-link">Users</a>
            <% } %>
            <a href="/viewEvents" class="nav-link">Events</a>
            <a href="/viewSurvey" class="nav-link">Survey</a>
            <a href="/viewAllMilestones" class="nav-link">Milestones</a>
            <a href="/viewAllDonations" class="nav-link">Donations</a>
        </div>

        <div class="nav-right">
            <% if (login) { %>
            <a href="/logout" class="nav-login">Log Out</a>
            <% } else { %>
            <a href="/login" class="nav-login">Login</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <header>
        <h1 class="site-title">Ella Rises</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Empowering young women to rise, learn & lead</p>
    </header>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="hero">
        <p>
            Welcome to Ella Rises — a community uplifting Latina youth to pursue higher education,
            embrace their cultural roots, and grow through arts, STEAM, and mentorship.
            Our mission is to build confidence, spark dreams, and open doors to opportunity.
        </p>

        <a href="/enroll" class="btn-main">Enroll Now</a>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;
        <a href="/donate" class="btn-main">Support Us</a>
    </div>

    <!-- PROGRAMS -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Our Programs</h2>

        <div class="programs">

            <div class="prog-card">
                <img src="/images/programs/ballet.png" class="prog-img" alt="Ballet Folklórico">
                <div class="prog-content">
                    <h3>Ballet Folklórico</h3>
                    <p>Dance rooted in culture — for creativity, confidence, and connection to heritage.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/programs/folklorico" class="btn-small">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="prog-card">
                <img src="/images/programs/mariachi.png" class="prog-img" alt="Mariachi">
                <div class="prog-content">
                    <h3>Mariachi</h3>
                    <p>All-girls mariachi band — honoring heritage while building performance skills.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/programs/mariachi" class="btn-small">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="prog-card">
                <img src="/images/programs/steam.png" class="prog-img" alt="STEAM Workshops">
                <div class="prog-content">
                    <h3>STEAM Workshops</h3>
                    <p>Science · Technology · Engineering · Arts · Math — hands-on learning experiences that spark curiosity.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/programs/steam" class="btn-small">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="prog-card">
                <img src="/images/programs/summit.png" class="prog-img" alt="Ella Rises Summit">
                <div class="prog-content">
                    <h3>Ella Rises Summit</h3>
                    <p>A day-camp blending art, STEM, leadership & campus tours — inspiring girls to prepare for college.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/programs/summit" class="btn-small">Learn More</a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="donate-bg">
        <div class="donate-card">
            <h2>Make a Difference</h2>
            <p>
                Your support helps uplift Latina youth through arts, STEAM, cultural pride, 
                confidence building, and mentorship.
            </p>

            <div class="donate-buttons">
                <a href="/donate" class="btn-donateD">Donate</a>
                <a href="/impact" class="btn-impactD">Your Impact</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- WHY ELLA RISES -->
    <div class="section" style="text-align: center;">
        <h2>Why Ella Rises</h2>
        <p style="max-width: 700px; margin: auto; color: #3A3F3B; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Many Latina girls face unique challenges: balancing cultural expectations, navigating school systems, 
            and dreaming big while honoring their heritage. Ella Rises offers a safe space of mentorship, creativity, 
            and community — so every girl can rise with confidence, purpose, and pride.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer>
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Ella Rises. 
        All rights reserved. 
        &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a> 
        &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>